	]em
	" and was released for the ZX Spectrum, Commodore 64, and BBC Micro computer systems. Like in the show, you play as Granny Smith, an old lady with superpowers granted by a magic ray who goes out to fight crime as "Super Gran". In this game, her mission is to stop her archenemy Scunner Campbell after he commits a robbery on a museum and return the artifacts he has stolen to their owners.
